   Jason Isbell reflects on divorce in 'Foxes in the Snow' Jason Isbell
   sings about his split from musician Amanda Shires on his latest album
   Foxes in the Snow. "What I was attempting to do is document a very
   specific time where I was going through a lot of changes," he says.

       Fresh Air
       NPR
